song.title: Sunny Ensemble
song.info: Well well well!!! .. what do we have here!? a MAJOR audiphile package for all you out there! and guess what, i'm glad to share this opportunity with all other musicians on this disk to give you a great juicy audiophile enjoyment! this song has been made for a special wii game which unluckily isn't out yet. made for all them ladies liking the happy / sunny vibe while working out ;) .. .peace .. tEiS out!
